text: The Digicel Cup may mean one of several sporting competitions sponsored by Digicel: *The Caribbean Cup (2004-2008), a national association football tournament. *The Papua New Guinea National Rugby League competition (2011-present), a national club rugby league competition. *The Cayman Islands Digicel Cup, a national club association football competition. *The Digicel Cup (rugby), a national club rugby union competition. *The Taça Digicel (Digicel Cup in English), an East Timorese football competition
title: Digicel Cup
